ris, like every other wrestling fan in T-Mobile Center that weekend, said he showed up unsure how Carter would perform.\", \"from\": 5550, \"to\": 5671, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5593, \"end\": 5608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/T-Mobile_Center\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"T-Mobile Center\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/T-Mobile_Center\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/T-Mobile_Center\"}, {\"begin\": 5652, \"end\": 5658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"score\": 0.9999688866811957, \"rank\": 3.111428690522104e-05, \"text\": \"Carter\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every other wrestling fan\", \"from\": 5562, \"to\": 5587}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He hoped that mentally the injury would not bog down his mind.\", \"from\": 5672, \"to\": 5734, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the injury\", \"from\": 5695, \"to\": 5705}, {\"ngram\": \"his mind\", \"from\": 5725, \"to\": 5733}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He even wondered how much sleep Carter had gotten in the previous weeks because he had been so dedicated to rehabbing.\", \"from\": 5735, \"to\": 5853, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5763, \"end\": 5768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Insomnia\", \"score\": 0.9975801194469354, \"rank\": 0.0024257503149924422, \"text\": \"sleep\", \"types\": [\"Q12136\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Insomnia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Insomnia\"}, {\"begin\": 5769, \"end\": 5775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"score\": 0.9999688866811957, \"rank\": 3.111428690522104e-05, \"text\": \"Carter\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"dbpedia\": \