25, \"to\": 7934}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He would come home from school and head to his room.\", \"from\": 7937, \"to\": 7989, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 7961, \"to\": 7967}, {\"ngram\": \"his room\", \"from\": 7980, \"to\": 7988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chris worried about his son's mental health until one day Carter came out of the room and had mapped out several changes.\", \"from\": 7990, \"to\": 8111, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8050, \"end\": 8056, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"score\": 0.9999688866811957, \"rank\": 3.111428690522104e-05, \"text\": \"Carter\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his son's mental health\", \"from\": 8010, \"to\": 8033}, {\"ngram\": \"one day\", \"from\": 8040, \"to\": 8047}, {\"ngram\": \"the room\", \"from\": 8067, \"to\": 8075}, {\"ngram\": \"several changes\", \"from\": 8095, \"to\": 8110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was quitting football - which until then was his top sport, Chris said - and was committing himself to being the best wrestler.\", \"from\": 8112, \"to\": 8242, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"football\", \"from\": 8128, \"to\": 8136}, {\"ngram\": \"his top sport\", \"from\": 8160, \"to\": 8173}, {\"ngram\": \"Chris\", \"from\": 8175, \"to\": 8180}, {\"ngram\": \"the best wrestler\", \"from\": 8224, \"to\": 8241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He told me what foods to buy, what kind of practice schedule he wanted to do,\\\" Chris said.\", \"from\": 8244, \"to\": 8335, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"what foods\", \"from\": 8256, \"to\": 8266}, {\"ngram\": \"what kind\", \"from\": 8275, \"to\": 8284}, {\"ngram\": \"practice schedule\", \"from\": 8288, \"to\": 8305}, {\"ngram\": \"Chris\", \"from\": 8324, \"to\": 8329}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He said, 'Stop buying this stuff, stop buying that stuff.\", \"from\": 8336, \"to\": 8394, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this stuff\", \"from\": 8359, \"to\": 8369}, {\"ngram\": \"that stuff\", \"from\": 8383, \"to\": 8393}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the stuff I need you to have in the house, Dad, and if you can not do it, I will go live with somebody else.'\\\"\", \"from\": 8395, \"to\": 8513, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the stuff\", \"from\": 8403, \"to\": 8412}, {\"ngram\": \"the house\", \"from\": 8435, \"to\": 8444}, {\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 8497, \"to\": 8505}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The football coach called and asked if Carter would reconsider.\", \"from\": 8515, \"to\": 8578, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8556, \"end\": 8562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"score\": 0.9999688866811957, \"rank\": 3.111428690522104e-05, \"text\": \"Carter\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The football coach\", \"from\": 8515, \"to\": 8533}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It wasn't up for discussion.\", \"from\": 8579, \"to\": 8607, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"discussion\", \"from\": 8596, \"to\": 8606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pizza, wings, Doritos, cakes, sweets and occasional fast food would have to go.\", \"from\": 8608, \"to\": 8687, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8624, \"end\": 8631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doritos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Doritos\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doritos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doritos\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pizza\", \"from\": 8608, \"to\": 8613}, {\"ngram\": \"wings\", \"from\": 8615, \"to\": 8620}, {\"ngram\": \"cakes\", \"from\": 8631, \"to\": 8636}, {\"ngram\": \"sweets\", \"from\": 8638, \"to\": 8644}, {\"ngram\": \"occasional fast food\", \"from\": 8649, \"to\": 8669}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He'd eat better meals and organic foods.\", \"from\": 8688, \"to\": 8728, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"better meals\", \"from\": 8697, \"to\": 8709}, {\"ngram\": \"organic foods\", \"from\": 8714, \"to\": 8727}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chris, with the exception of hiding occasional treats from his son, would also eat better to help Carter with his plan.\", \"from\": 8729, \"to\": 8848, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8829, \"end\": 8835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"score\": 0.9999688866811957, \"rank\": 3.111428690522104e-05, \"text\": \"Carter\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the exception\", \"from\": 8741, \"to\": 8754}, {\"ngram\": \"occasional treats\", \"from\": 8765, \"to\": 8782}, {\"ngram\": \"his son\", \"from\": 8788, \"to\": 8795}, {\"ngram\": \"his plan\", \"from\": 8839, \"to\": 8847}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He'd finish as a state runner-up as a sophomore before winning titles in his junior and senior years.\", \"from\": 8849, \"to\": 8950, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a state runner-up\", \"from\": 8864, \"to\": 8881}, {\"ngram\": \"a sophomore\", \"from\": 8885, \"to\": 8896}, {\"ngram\": \"titles\", \"from\": 8912, \"to\": 8918}, {\"ngram\": \"his junior and senior years\", \"from\": 8922, \"to\": 8949}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think we gotta take him for his word when he says he does not do this for championships and titles,\\\" Chris said.\", \"from\": 8952, \"to\": 9067, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his word\", \"from\": 8983, \"to\": 8991}, {\"ngram\": \"championships\", \"from\": 9029, \"to\": 9042}, {\"ngram\": \"titles\", \"from\": 9047, \"to\": 9053}, {\"ngram\": \"Chris\", \"from\": 9056, \"to\": 9061}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He does it to know that there is not another man that can beat him, and I think that's what motivates him.\", \"from\": 9068, \"to\": 9175, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another man\", \"from\": 9106, \"to\": 9117}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think, in his mind, when he takes somebody out he expects that, he's proud of that, and then he's on to the next one.\\\"\", \"from\": 9176, \"to\": 9296, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his mind\", \"from\": 9188, \"to\": 9196}, {\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 9212, \"to\": 9220}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In this case, the next challenge will be as grueling as they come.\", \"from\": 9298, \"to\": 9364, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this case\", \"from\": 9301, \"to\": 9310}, {\"ngram\": \"the next challenge\", \"from\": 9312, \"to\": 9330}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Between cutting 11 pounds and wrestling against the best in the nation while not at full health, it'll be a long shot to try and pull off an Olympic berth.\", \"from\": 9365, \"to\": 9520, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"11 pounds\", \"from\": 9381, \"to\": 9390}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation\", \"from\": 9425, \"to\": 9435}, {\"ngram\": \"full health\", \"from\": 9449, \"to\": 9460}, {\"ngram\": \"a long shot\", \"from\": 9471, \"to\": 9482}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic berth\", \"from\": 9503, \"to\": 9519}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Starocci is not wired to think this way and never has been.\", \"from\": 9522, \"to\": 9585, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Starocci\", \"from\": 9526, \"to\": 9534}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's why Chris is certain Carter is again dialed in, busy mapping out the most important wrestling plan of his career.\", \"from\": 9586, \"to\": 9704, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9614, \"end\": 9620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"score\": 0.9999688866811957, \"rank\": 3.111428690